  <description>In a huddle around their soft drinks at the University of Chicago &quot;hot spot&quot; in Mandel Hall is a group of girl students out for a night of fun. Only liquids of the &quot;Sunday School Cocktail&quot; variety are sold in the club, which operates on a basis that any profits will benefit the students themselves. Clockwise, from left center are: Margaret Argall, Marjorie Schulz; Florine Phillips, Donna Culliton, Mary Dickey, Mary Fairbanks and Natalie Kline.</description>
